ty of his output was in poetic form he has rarely been treated as a source for the biblical text. The present study brings together all the identifiable references to the Gospels in Gregory’s writings for the first time, comparing them with standard biblical texts and manuscripts in order to determine their significance for the history and transmission of the New Testament. This collection also sheds new light on Gregory’s treatment of Scripture and the distinctive role it plays in his rhetorical style.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aChristian literature, EarlyxHistory and criticism. 4aChristianity. 4aLiterature. 4aReligion. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / Literature & the Arts.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishz978311099454408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022z9783110994537oZDB-23-DGF08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076710040uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/978146324338840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463243388423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463243388/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076710-0  Gorgias Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099454-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBK